rino problem and even\nthe large angle solution of the solar neutrino problem. It would further,\nalready in a first step, cover almost the full MSSM parameter space for\nprediction of neutralinos as cold dark matter, making the experiment\ncompetitive to LHC in the search for supersymmetry.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Feb 1998 16:20:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
